17
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,480
You're not hungry?

18
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,200
Let's eat it later.

19
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,510
Sit down.

20
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,230
Sit.

21
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,680
Take a look

22
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,840
at this.

23
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,640
Didn't they run out of my size

24
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,360
