28
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,150
Thanks, Mom.

29
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,310
When can we go skating?

30
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,800
Yi,

31
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,870
I actually came back

32
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,520
