35
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,470
I recently

36
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,840
took on a big project for the company.

37
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,470
My superior wants

38
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:43,080
to send me abroad for a period of time.

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:46,120
When I return, I'll get promoted to
the position of team leader.

40
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,960
This is a rare opportunity.

41
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,080
I don't want to miss it.

42
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,430
Well,

43
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,870
no wonder you bought takeout and skates.

44
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:05,800
So this is what you want to tell me.

45
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:07,470
No.

46
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:10,150
I really missed you.

47
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,630
I came back to see you.

48
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,840
We won't be seeing each other

49
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,840
for a long time.

50
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,360
How long will you be gone?

51
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,190
Tentatively,

52
