53
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:30,840
When is your flight?

54
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:33,430
Tonight.

55
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:36,360
Sure.

56
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,430
Go if you want.

57
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:39,750
