58
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,710
I'll bring you there.

59
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,360
No need.

60
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,590
Yi,

61
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,910
I've reheated the food.

62
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,360
Come out and eat some.

63
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,680
If you don't come out soon,

64
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,120
I'm leaving.

65
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,750
Yi.

66
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,270
I know

67
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,560
we can't

68
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,510
keep you company every day

69
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,830
like normal parents

70
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,750
and watch you grow up.

71
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,630
But we're

72
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:29,600
doing this for our family.

73
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,800
