74
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,480
but you'll understand in the future.

75
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:41,070
Won't you come out to see me?

76
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:43,160
I'm fine.

77
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,190
You should leave!

78
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,720
Okay.

79
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:52,040
Take good care of yourself.

80
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,000
When we're not around,

81
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,310
