87
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,720
We're going

88
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,800
precisely because
you don't know how to skate.

89
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,040
They insisted on going,

90
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,430
but I don't know how to skate.

91
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,190
