96
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,600
I'll have to stay at home
to do my homework.

97
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,430
I don't have to do my homework.

98
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,310
I'm not going.

99
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:45,680
Does this still count?

100
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:47,950
Hey,

101
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:49,240
are you sure
you want to use the wish card

102
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,510
on this?

103
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,630
Yes.

104
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,070
If you remain silent,
I'll take it as a yes.

105
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:56,070
See you at the basketball court
under the bridge tomorrow.

106
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:57,040
Don't stand me up!

107
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,240
Hey!

108
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,800
