274
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:21,720
Take a break.

275
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,630
What if you pull your back?

276
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,240
I'm fine, Mom.

277
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,240
