280
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:31,600
My biggest wish

281
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,320
is that in the future,

282
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,150
you'll never have
to carry a single box of it.

283
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:33,960
Give it to me.

284
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:37,480
Mom.

285
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:39,510
My biggest wish

286
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,750
is that

287
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:41,910
you don't have to carry any water, ever.

288
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:44,120
As long as you live well,

289
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,550
I can do anything.

290
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:46,750
Come, give it to me.

291
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,320
(Xu.)

292
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:53,600
You're here.

293
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,080
I see you have
new pomelos at the entrance.

294
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,030
Let me pick two.

295
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,120
They've just arrived.

296
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,790
