298
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,600
Your mom talks about you every day.

299
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:06,240
I heard that you're a doctoral student.

300
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,480
What a promising young man.

301
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,630
There are only a few doctoral students

302
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:11,080
in the whole of Hangtian City.

303
00:16:11,550 --> 00:16:12,870
You taught him well.

304
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:13,320
In the future,

305
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,750
you'll live comfortably.

306
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:17,480
I'm a primary school graduate.
What can I teach him?

307
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:19,000
It was all his own efforts.

308
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:21,440
Well, you also have contributed
to this achievement.

309
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:23,240
In "The Legend of White Snake,"

310
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,320
even the mother of a top scholar

311
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,390
can get a title.

312
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,240
Zhuang Yuan

313
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:28,790
rhymes with

314
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:29,790
zhuangyuan, also the top scholar.

315
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,080
Goodbye.

316
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,390
Okay.

317
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:37,120
Xu, I'll leave you to it.

318
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:37,790
I'm leaving.

319
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:38,480
Come again.

320
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,080
Okay.

321
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:43,390
Mom.

322
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:45,840
Stop showing me off in front of others.

323
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,750
What if I fail

324
00:16:47,750 --> 00:16:48,670
to graduate?

325
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,510
There are no "ifs."

326
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,870
I'm still looking forward to the day

327
00:16:53,870 --> 00:16:55,200
when I can see you

328
00:16:55,510 --> 00:16:56,750
in your graduation gown.

329
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,720
I'll be so proud!

330
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:02,030
(Sir,)

331
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:04,270
actually, I haven't decided

332
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:07,550
if pursuing an academic career
is the path I want to take.

333
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:09,790
It's not just about whether you can
pursue an academic career or not.

334
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,680
It's a matter of
whether or not your thesis can pass

335
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,270
and if you can graduate smoothly,

336
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,310
get it?

337
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,680
I'm not like Guan Chao's dad,

338
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,070
who isn't even showing up

339
00:17:20,070 --> 00:17:21,240
at his son's wedding,

340
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,550
which is such an important event.

341
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,960
Why isn't his dad coming?

342
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:28,750
I think Guan Chao
didn't even invite him.

343
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:42,680
Ms. Fang,

344
00:17:43,070 --> 00:17:44,110
if there's nothing else,

345
00:17:44,110 --> 00:17:45,160
we're

346
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:46,720
getting off work.

347
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,920
You're leaving together?

348
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:48,960
Yes.

349
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,590
We're having dinner together.

350
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,590
Have fun.

351
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,310
Okay, Ms. Fang.

352
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:55,030
See you on Monday.

353
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,240
Are we not going
to ask Ms. Fang to join us for dinner?

354
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,000
Are you crazy?

355
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,070
You can ask her if you want.

356
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:02,000
I won't go.

357
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:06,720
Slow down.

358
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:08,640
There are plenty in the pot.

359
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:11,480
You've all lost weight.

360
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,480
Did you not eat well out there

361
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,790
or are you too tired?

362
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:15,550
Of course.

363
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:16,750
Not getting to eat your wontons

364
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:18,110
made us starve and lose weight.

365
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:20,440
Isn't Mingyu coming back?

366
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,920
Mingyu is busy with work.

367
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:29,109
She hasn't been back in a while.

368
00:18:29,109 --> 00:18:30,309
During New Year,

369
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,829
she was busy with work

370
00:18:31,829 --> 00:18:32,999
and didn't come back.

371
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:34,880
Grandma,

372
00:18:35,349 --> 00:18:36,549
do you want to see her?

373
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:50,720
Mingyu.

374
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:51,960
Grandma?

375
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,440
Yingzi and the rest are back.

376
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,440
You're the only one missing.

377
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,160
Are you busy?

378
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:00,830
It's fine.

379
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,270
It's good to be busy.

380
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,960
Do take care of yourself

381
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,270
out there.

382
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,960
Don't get too tired.

383
00:19:08,030 --> 00:19:09,070
If you want to come back,

384
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:10,680
you can come back anytime.

385
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:13,830
I'll cook wontons for you.

386
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:17,160
Got it, Grandma.

387
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,070
Mingyu,

388
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,440
you're disloyal.

389
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,480
Even Zhuang Yuan is back.

390
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,440
Why are you not back?

391
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,110
It's fine, Mingyu.

392
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:26,720
I'll bring
the wedding candy to you later.

393
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,030
Got it.

394
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:31,880
Mingyu.

395
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:34,240
Look

396
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,000
at this.

397
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,110
It's late.

398
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:40,310
Are you still working overtime?

399
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:42,440
It's nothing.

400
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:44,310
Grandma missed you

401
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:45,310
and wanted to see you.

402
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:49,310
You should get back to work.

403
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:50,920
Bye.

404
00:20:05,790 --> 00:20:07,240
It'd be great if Yifei were here.

405
00:20:08,270 --> 00:20:09,160
Yes.

406
00:20:10,110 --> 00:20:13,000
I wonder if she's doing well overseas.

407
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:14,960
Grandma,

408
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:17,200
performing overseas is her dream.

409
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:18,160
Otherwise,

410
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:19,960
she'll definitely come back.

411
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:22,920
I just saw her.

412
00:20:23,270 --> 00:20:25,790
She's in a great condition.
Neither fat nor skinny.

413
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,510
Don't worry.

414
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,510
She said

415
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:29,720
when she comes back,

416
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,240
she'll bring us
to watch her performance.

417
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:32,960
Okay, I won't worry.

418
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,480
You've all grown up.

419
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:37,830
You're no longer the kids back then.

420
00:20:38,110 --> 00:20:38,880
Of course not.

421
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,070
To you,

422
00:20:40,070 --> 00:20:41,880
we'll always be kids.

423
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:47,920
Here.

424
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,400
Enjoy your meal.

425
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:49,750
Okay.

426
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,480
Let me know if you need anything.

427
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,200
Thank you, sir.

428
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,240
Say,

429
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:55,110
Yang Fan's family is doing well, right?

430
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:57,830
Why is she marrying Guan Chao?

431
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,400
Who knows?

432
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:00,790
She insists on marrying him,

433
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,270
but Guan Chao

434
00:21:02,270 --> 00:21:04,350
can only provide a dorm on campus.

435
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:07,590
Wasn't the house renovated
from an old one?

436
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:08,270
Yes.

437
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:09,960
Using that as their marital home

438
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,510
is so sad.

439
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:13,270
Most importantly,

440
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:14,510
Guan Chao's dad

441
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:17,270
isn't giving any money.

442
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:19,960
Will they live a good life?

443
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:23,550
What does my son getting married
have anything to do with you?

444
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,030
Guan,

445
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:25,920
I'm sorry.

446
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,720
I didn't see you there.

447
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:28,880
I think you didn't see me on purpose.

448
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:30,200
Why are you scolding me?

449
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,830
I'm hitting you.

450
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:33,070
How dare you?

451
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:35,640
Guan.

452
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:37,960
Guan.

453
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,030
What are you doing?

454
00:21:39,270 --> 00:21:40,000
Don't stop me!

455
00:21:44,070 --> 00:21:44,750
Yang Fan's call.

456
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:45,590
I need to answer this.

457
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:50,480
What are you talking about?

458
00:21:52,590 --> 00:21:53,750
So what if I hit you?

459
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,110
I'm going to kick you!

460
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:55,440
Dad,

461
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,270
what are you doing?

462
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:58,350
Is your dad mentally ill?

463
00:21:58,350 --> 00:21:59,590
We were chatting,

464
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:01,310
but he suddenly came over and hit me.

465
00:22:01,310 --> 00:22:02,440
Chatting? Nonsense!

466
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:02,960
Dad.

467
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:04,480
Don't you know?

468
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,270
Dad!

469
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:06,880
Can you stop?

470
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:09,200
Dad,

471
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,270
let's go back.

472
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:11,640
Yes, go back.

473
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,590
Did you know what he said?

474
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:13,480
Did you know?

475
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:14,680
Okay...

476
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:15,750
Are you hurt?

477
00:22:21,350 --> 00:22:22,310
I'm really sorry.

478
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:24,590
He acts this way when he's drunk.

479
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:26,070
That doesn't mean
he can hit me for no reason!

480
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:28,270
Are you okay?

481
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:29,640
His head is bleeding.

482
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,480
How is he fine?

483
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:31,680
I'm really sorry.

484
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:32,750
If you need us to compensate

485
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:33,590
any medical expenses,

486
00:22:33,590 --> 00:22:34,480
please let us know.

487
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,160
Fine, then.

488
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,440
Are you Chen Chen's parents?

489
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,350
Mr. Guan.

490
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,510
Yes, it's me.

491
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,110
Since my son is in your class,

492
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:47,880
we won't make a police report.

493
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,440
No.

494
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,030
If this happens again,

495
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,030
call the police

496
00:22:51,030 --> 00:22:52,440
and let them handle the matter.

497
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,590
What are you talking about?

498
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,510
Let's go.

499
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:32,310
Didn't you say
the monthly exam was canceled?

500
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:33,880
Yes,

501
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,200
it was canceled.

502
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,510
But why did Han Dong's son

503
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,310
ask him to sign the exam papers?

504
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:41,400
I don't know.

505
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:47,510
You've grown up, huh?

506
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:48,550
Not only are you
failing in your studies,

507
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,550
but now you've also
learned to lie, right?

508
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:52,830
I work hard to provide you
with food and shelter,

509
00:23:53,360 --> 00:23:54,440
and this is how you treat me?

510
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,680
Is there anything else
you're hiding from me?

511
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,030
No.

512
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:09,000
I'll give you another chance.

513
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,350
Are you hiding anything else from me?

514
00:24:11,350 --> 00:24:13,000
No. Really.

515
00:24:16,110 --> 00:24:16,750
Let me ask you.

516
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:19,510
What are you doing
in Jiangzhou this weekend?

517
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:32,510
Were you looking for this?

518
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:35,110
Give it back to me!

519
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:38,110
Why are you going to Jiangzhou?

520
00:24:38,110 --> 00:24:39,030
Give it back to me!

521
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:40,240
Why are you going to Jiangzhou?

522
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:42,430
You want to find your mom, right?

523
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,960
Your mom doesn't want you anymore.

524
00:24:44,270 --> 00:24:46,000
She doesn't want our family anymore.

525
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:46,880
What are you doing?

526
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:48,680
Give it to me!

527
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:49,880
Move!

528
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,350
Stop dreaming!

529
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:53,960
If it weren't for you,

530
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,960
would my mom have left?

531
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:56,440
How dare you talk to me this way?

532
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,750
Was I wrong?

533
00:24:59,590 --> 00:25:01,200
Mom left because you hit her.

534
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:02,640
If it weren't for me,

535
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,720
she would've left ages ago.

536
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:04,880
Hit me!

537
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,750
Your abuse destroyed our family!

538
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:08,270
How dare you talk to me this way?

539
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:09,400
Say that again!

540
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,510
No one can stand staying with you.

541
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:12,720
I regretted

542
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,920
not leaving with Mom back then.

543
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,830
Let go!

544
00:25:18,830 --> 00:25:19,960
Stand right there!

545
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:21,790
Let go!

546
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:40,480
Mom.

547
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:42,000
Chao,

548
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,030
what's wrong?

549
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:45,720
Did something happen?

550
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:47,920
Nothing.

551
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,000
I haven't called you in a while.

552
00:25:52,030 --> 00:25:53,200
I want to talk to you.

553
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,000
Did your dad hit you again?

554
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:55,880
No.

555
00:25:56,510 --> 00:25:57,550
I'm taller

556
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:58,310
and bulkier than him now.

557
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,550
Even if he wants to hit me, he can't.

558
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:02,640
Good.

559
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,030
How are you doing recently?

560
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,070
I've been working hard.

561
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:09,030
My 100-meter record
has improved by 0.2 seconds.

562
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:09,640
Besides,

563
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:10,000
I...

564
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,830
Mom? Mom!

565
00:26:11,790 --> 00:26:12,550
Be good, Xing.

566
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:13,350
Stop crying.

567
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:14,510
I'll be there soon.

568
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:15,510
Guan Chao,

569
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:16,680
I'll call you later.

570
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,480
I need to go now.

571
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:34,240
I know you're still awake.

572
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,240
Do you have any shame?

573
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,830
Others have to clean up your mess

574
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:38,400
every day.

575
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,350
That's enough,

576
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,400
Chao.

577
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,030
Stop talking.

578
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,640
Yang Fan,

579
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,400
someone who pretends
to be asleep will never wake up.

580
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:46,720
You deserve
to live in this rubbish dump.

581
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:47,590
That's enough.

582
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:48,440
After my mom left,

583
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,510
he never woke up.

584
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:50,550
Besides drinking and fighting,

585
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,640
what else can you do?

586
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,640
Stop, Chao.

587
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:53,200
I must be crazy

588
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,880
to care for you.

589
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,240
I shouldn't have cared about you.

590
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,240
Stop talking.

591
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:01,480
If you want to lie down,
don't get up, ever!

592
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:03,160
Look at you.

593
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,590
