608
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,310
(hidden in ordinary moments.)

609
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:51,480
Ding Ye's book is amazing.

610
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,790
I can't believe
it's an alternate reality.

611
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:56,880
