616
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:09,350
I didn't see her.

617
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,070
Zhu Baoming.

618
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:13,920
Where is Zhuang Yuan?

619
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:15,030
I don't know.

620
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:41,400
Grandma,

621
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,510
