622
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:46,350
You didn't come back with them?

623
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:47,110
No.

624
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,750
They disappeared.

625
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:51,110
That... That's strange.

626
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,120
I heard

627
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,240
they went to Jiang Yi's house.

628
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,070
Why would they go to Jiang Yi's house?

629
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,030
I don't know.

630
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,200
Got it.

631
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,480
Grandma, I'm leaving.

632
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:05,440
Slow... Slow down!

633
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,030
Ugh, Jiang Yi.

634
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:29,160
I told you to change the light bulb
but you didn't.

635
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:29,920
How lazy of you.

636
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:41,070
Jiang Yi.

637
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:49,830
Jiang Yi?

638
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:54,960
Jiang Yi.

639
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,960
Jiang Yi, don't scare me.

640
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,030
Jiang Yi!

641
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:35,510
Happy birthday!

642
00:30:35,790 --> 00:30:36,350
You...

643
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:38,270
You all...

644
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,790
What is this?

645
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:40,960
Are you happy?

646
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:42,880
Yes.

647
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,720
