650
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,720
If we had told you beforehand,
would that be a surprise?

651
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,350
Okay.

652
00:30:50,350 --> 00:30:51,070
I thought

653
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:52,880
I wouldn't get
to celebrate my birthday this year.

654
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:54,960
My mom told me to focus on my studies.

655
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,750
