671
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,310
Jiang Yi is here.

672
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:29,680
How could you compare to him?

673
00:31:36,350 --> 00:31:37,160
Jiang Yi,

674
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:39,200
I didn't mean that.

675
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,400
I was too upset by her results.

676
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,110
Huang Yingzi,

677
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:43,590
