689
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:57,350
No.

690
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,240
No...

691
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,110
I just want to celebrate my birthday.

692
00:32:03,110 --> 00:32:05,030
There's time.
I want to celebrate my birthday.

693
00:32:05,030 --> 00:32:05,750
Talk properly.

694
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,350
What's wrong
with celebrating my birthday?

695
00:32:07,350 --> 00:32:08,160
Do you hear me?

696
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,240
Talk properly.

697
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:15,070
Remember your promise
before school started?

698
00:32:15,070 --> 00:32:16,960
You told me, "Don't worry, Mom.

699
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,680
I'll rank in the top ten
in the exams.

700
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,240
I'll do well!"

701
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,640
Did you forget?

702
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,440
I didn't forget.

703
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,920
I said that.

704
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:27,720
Fine.

705
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:30,590
I keep my word.

706
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,680
I won't celebrate my birthday, then.

707
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,240
Good.

708
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,510
Excellent.

709
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,160
Are you really not celebrating it?

710
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,030
Yes.

711
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:54,550
When I enter college,

712
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,640
I'll celebrate my birthday every day.

713
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:00,680
Good.

714
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:03,160
You don't need to waste money,

715
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,070
right?

716
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,640
(Ande look at her now.)

717
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:10,070
Does it seem like
she's okay with not celebrating it?

718
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:10,880
For girls,

719
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,440
when they say "it's okay,"
it usually means it's not okay,

720
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,200
