724
00:33:16,550 --> 00:33:17,960
In the future, you won't have
to worry about finding a girlfriend.

725
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:18,440
Zhuang Yuan,

726
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:20,000
it's not that Jiang Yi knows girls well,

727
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,110
he just knows Huang Yingzi well.

728
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:23,440
What do you mean?

729
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,400
Are you saying that I'm not a girl?

730
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:26,200
I know you well.

731
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:26,720
Since young,

732
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:27,720
