735
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:30,310
I didn't mean it.

736
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,070
I swear.

737
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:32,880
That's tactful of you.

738
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,830
But

739
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:34,830
where did you get

740
00:33:34,830 --> 00:33:36,440
so many cute words?

741
00:33:36,440 --> 00:33:37,830
Jiang said

742
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:38,720
you like

743
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,270
shiny stuff.

744
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:40,960
The three of us

745
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:42,640
