to prepare this.

746
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,720
Unbelievable.

747
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,480
Thank you.

748
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:45,480
I'm touched.

749
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,720
I like it a lot.

750
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,480
I announce

751
00:33:47,830 --> 00:33:49,270
that the surprise is a success!

752
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:50,920
Now,

753
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,070
