754
00:33:55,110 --> 00:33:55,830
Here.

755
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:57,350
This can be installed
on the front of your bicycle.

756
00:33:57,350 --> 00:33:58,960
You won't have to worry about the lack
of streetlights when riding at night.

757
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,510
Thank you.

758
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:03,550
It's perfect for my Blue.

759
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:09,840
You can blast Stefanie Sun's songs

760
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:11,510
