761
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:12,880
I'll never have to fight with my dad

762
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,000
for the speaker anymore.

763
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:15,590
Don't play the music too loud

764
00:34:15,590 --> 00:34:17,110
and disturb me when I play games.

765
00:34:17,110 --> 00:34:18,960
Consider it an honor
that my precious speaker

766
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:20,320
