767
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:22,400
Here, look at mine.

768
00:34:25,150 --> 00:34:27,000
Thank you.

769
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:29,480
Ding Ye's "Noctiluca."

770
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:31,230
My favorite author!

771
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,150
I know you, right?

772
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:33,920
Isn't your favorite author

773
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:35,630
Kafka?

774
00:34:36,030 --> 00:34:37,440
