775
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,760
Is there a difference?

776
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:40,920
Of course.

777
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:43,030
I admire Kafka

778
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:45,510
for his literary work.

779
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,510
Ding Ye is different.

780
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:50,110
He lives on earth,

781
00:34:50,110 --> 00:34:51,920
