I will get to know him.

782
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,880
We'll get to chat.

783
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,280
Perhaps

784
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,190
we can be good friends.

785
00:34:56,190 --> 00:34:57,110
Hey,

786
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,840
Ding Ye might not be willing

787
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:00,190
