795
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:30,960
Let me tell you.

796
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:33,590
This is not an ordinary globe.

797
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,960
How is it special?

798
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:36,960
It...

799
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:43,920
You'll know in the future.

800
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:49,710
Thank you.

801
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,400
I will take good care

802
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:53,110
