809
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:00,440
Hurry.

810
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:01,030
What is it?

811
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:01,550
What gift?

812
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,710
Wait here.

813
00:36:02,710 --> 00:36:03,150
Come on.

814
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,630
Why is it so mysterious?

815
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:06,480
Go in.

816
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:09,280
Well, what gift is it?

817
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:18,440
Come on out.

818
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,190
Hurry.

819
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:54,230
How is it?

820
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,360
Isn't she pretty?

821
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:59,070
I don't look good in dresses, right?

822
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:05,280
Of course not!

823
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:07,440
You're gorgeous!

824
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,030
Huang,

825
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,400
