878
00:39:49,030 --> 00:39:50,030
Who?

879
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,510
The doctoral student.

880
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:52,510
Zhuang Yuan?

881
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,920
I remember something.

882
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:56,230
During the summer of the Olympics,

883
00:39:56,230 --> 00:39:57,550
I saw Huang Yingzi

884
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:58,960
wearing a purple dress.

885
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:00,480
She was all dressed up.

886
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,800
I think she went on a date.

887
00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:03,480
I turned back and took a look.

888
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:04,360
Guess what?

889
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:07,000
It was Zhuang Yuan
waiting for Huang Yingzi

890
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:08,150
by the side of the road.

891
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,320
Zhuang Yuan?

892
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:13,630
Hong.

893
00:40:14,230 --> 00:40:14,670
Ling.

894
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:15,510
I'm exhausted.

895
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:16,880
Why? What's the rush?

896
00:40:17,590 --> 00:40:18,920
Is Zhuang Yuan around?

897
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:19,710
No.

898
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:22,880
He should be with Yingzi and Guan Chao.

899
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:23,840
Do you need to talk to him?

900
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:25,480
No, not him.

901
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,280
I'm here to talk to you.

902
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,400
How rare.

903
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:42,710
Yingzi,

904
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:43,400
you're up early.

905
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:44,440
Every morning, I wake up early

906
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:46,150
to go to work, okay?

907
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,190
Good.

908
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:47,800
Eat this.

909
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,800
After breakfast, let's go to the cafe.

910
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,920
Why are we going to the cafe?

911
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,110
You don't even drink coffee.

912
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:55,150
Young people like coffee, right?

913
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,800
Don't ask questions.

914
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,000
You'll find out soon.

915
00:40:59,030 --> 00:40:59,880
I can't today.

916
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:00,630
I have something else to do.

917
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:03,440
What is it?

918
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:05,190
You'll find out soon.

919
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:08,800
After you're done,

920
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:10,030
come to the cafe to look for me.

921
00:41:11,440 --> 00:41:13,000
How mysterious.

922
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,440
Okay, then.

923
00:41:16,710 --> 00:41:18,000
Yesterday, I told Yang Fan

924
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:19,480
I won't be there.

925
00:41:20,510 --> 00:41:21,710
Who told you I came here today

926
00:41:21,710 --> 00:41:23,480
to invite you to the wedding?

927
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:24,670
If you go,

928
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:26,480
I'm afraid
that you'll get drunk and hit others.

929
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:28,070
Why are you here, then?

930
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:30,440
I'm here to tell you

931
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:32,550
you started a fight
at the restaurant yesterday

932
00:41:32,870 --> 00:41:34,230
and need to compensate the owner.

933
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:35,360
You know that, right?

934
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,320
Mr. Fan said,

935
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,630
as you're neighbors,

936
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:40,030
he'll only ask you
to compensate 1000 yuan.

937
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:41,070
Nonsense!

938
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:42,150
Are those old tables and chairs

939
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:43,510
worth that much?

940
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:44,480
I'll go talk to him.

941
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,710
Calm down.

942
00:41:45,710 --> 00:41:46,710
I've already

943
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:47,800
paid him on behalf of you.

944
00:41:48,110 --> 00:41:50,360
Think of it
as my wedding gift to Guan Chao.

945
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:51,000
Also,

946
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,880
the customer you hit yesterday

947
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:54,320
is the parent of Guan Chao's student.

948
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:55,360
You know that, right?

949
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,840
How would I know who he is?

950
00:41:57,590 --> 00:41:59,190
Why is this so troublesome?

951
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:03,110
You broke his nose bridge.

952
00:42:03,110 --> 00:42:05,000
If he informs the school about this,

953
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,800
Guan Chao will lose his job.

954
00:42:07,230 --> 00:42:08,400
It isn't that serious.

955
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:09,670
He only bled a little, right?

956
00:42:09,670 --> 00:42:11,000
Besides, he also retaliated.

957
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,110
Tell him

958
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:14,880
to come to me if he wants anything.

959
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,960
Don't trouble my son.

960
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:18,190
Are you showing concern
for your son now?

961
00:42:23,480 --> 00:42:24,400
Don't worry.

962
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:26,670
The problem is solved.

963
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,840
Why are you here, then?

964
00:42:33,030 --> 00:42:34,280
I forgot.

965
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:36,000
I'm here to deliver a suit to you.

966
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:38,070
I bought you a suit.

967
00:42:38,070 --> 00:42:39,230
I thought

968
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:41,070
you'd be able to wear it at the wedding.

969
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:43,230
Yet, since you're not going,

970
00:42:43,230 --> 00:42:44,800
it doesn't matter anymore.

971
00:42:45,190 --> 00:42:46,320
I'll just leave it here.

972
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,510
Actually, it's fine if you don't go.

973
00:42:49,510 --> 00:42:52,000
It's not a big deal if you're not there.

974
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:54,320
But at the wedding,

975
00:42:54,320 --> 00:42:56,840
the bride's family members
will be at the main table,

976
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:57,710
including her parents.

977
00:42:58,070 --> 00:43:00,670
On the groom's side,
there won't be anyone.

978
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:03,360
There might be

979
00:43:03,360 --> 00:43:04,440
a few more gossiping people
like those from yesterday.

980
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,550
They will gossip

981
00:43:05,550 --> 00:43:06,550
just like yesterday.

982
00:43:06,550 --> 00:43:08,030
Who gave them the guts? I...

983
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:09,710
Why? Are you going to fight them?

984
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:12,400
I...

985
00:43:15,560 --> 00:43:16,590
Mr. Guan,

986
00:43:16,590 --> 00:43:17,710
I know

987
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:19,190
that deep down,

988
00:43:19,190 --> 00:43:21,000
you actually care about Guan Chao.

989
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:22,360
You started a fight yesterday

990
00:43:22,360 --> 00:43:23,440
because those two people

991
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:24,510
were gossiping about Guan Chao

992
00:43:24,510 --> 00:43:26,000
and Yang Fan, right?

993
00:43:27,230 --> 00:43:28,480
If you care about him,

994
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,070
why don't you tell him in person?

995
00:43:33,630 --> 00:43:34,800
What for?

996
00:43:34,800 --> 00:43:35,760
Well, I...

997
00:43:38,150 --> 00:43:40,070
Both of you are funny.

998
00:43:40,070 --> 00:43:41,320
You care about each other

999
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:42,320
but refuse to say anything.

1000
00:43:42,670 --> 00:43:44,400
Yesterday, to take care of you,

1001
00:43:44,400 --> 00:43:45,840
Guan Chao didn't even
attend the wedding rehearsal.

1002
00:43:46,400 --> 00:43:47,670
He didn't say it out loud,

1003
00:43:47,670 --> 00:43:48,710
but I know

1004
00:43:48,710 --> 00:43:50,190
he wants you

1005
00:43:50,190 --> 00:43:51,550
to attend his wedding.

1006
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:00,440
Okay.

1007
00:44:00,440 --> 00:44:01,230
I've said everything.

1008
00:44:01,840 --> 00:44:03,190
I'm taking my leave now.

1009
00:44:04,190 --> 00:44:05,230
You can decide

1010
00:44:05,230 --> 00:44:07,800
whether or not
you want to wear this suit.

1011
00:44:08,590 --> 00:44:09,840
Goodbye, Mr. Guan.

1012
00:44:11,710 --> 00:44:12,800
Goodbye, Yingzi.
